PR DESCRIPTION:
The purpose of this refactoring is to allow extensions to contribute components to an application SBOM.

The core of Quarkus contributes Maven dependencies and packaging details. Other extensions, such as Quinoa, Web Bundler, etc could use `SbomContributionBuildItem` to contribute npm components they manage.

